<node TEXT="Deep Wizardry: Stack Unwinding. May 14 2013. This weekend I budgeted &#x201c;a few hours&#x201d; to learn about stack unwinding but oh what a journey down the rabbit hole it became. This esoteric topic lies at the intersection of compilers linkers loaders debuggers ABIs and language runtimes. There is precious little documentation about it and " ID="ID_1818701841" CREATED="1569323920135" MODIFIED="1569323920135"/>
