<node TEXT="Unlike early binding late binding allows you to create programs that can respond to events occurring while the program executes without having to create a large amount of contingency code. Keep in mind that because a function call is not resolved until run time late binding can make for somewhat slower execution times." ID="ID_1529915964" CREATED="1569323920145" MODIFIED="1569323920145"/>
</node>
